                        We accept customized cakes, cupcakes, & more! Order now!
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Division 2 -->
                <div class="divisions col mb-4">
                    <h5 class="heading-bottom" style="font-family: Poppins ExtraBold;">Contact Us</h5>
                    <ul class="nav flex-column">
